reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good personalized gift
reviews.reviewText: I recently snagged this Water Bottle Carrier Bag with a Phone Pocket for my bestie, and it's the ultimate on-the-go companion! The chenille initial gives it a personalized touch, and the black color is sleek and versatile. The adjustable crossbody strap makes it super convenient for traveling, hiking, or camping – hands-free and stylish. The phone pocket is a genius addition, keeping everything in one place. It's like a cozy home for their Stanley 40oz tumbler. The quality is top-notch, and the design is not just practical but also looks great. If you're searching for a thoughtful and functional gift for a friend who's always on the move, this water bottle carrier is a winner. It's become my bestie's go-to accessory for staying hydrated in style!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My daughter loves this!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my daughter to take with us on our Spring Break. My daughter’s water tumbler goes everywhere with her and this will allow her to keep her things organized and together. This water bottle carrier bag so cute and well made. The color is so pretty! It has a pocket for your phone and an additional pocket for whatever else you need. My daughter keeps her money, debit card, ID, chapstick and key in the extra packet so it is very roomy. The strap is adjustable to a length that you can wear it as a regular bag or crossbody. It fits my daughters 40 ounce Stanley tumblers and her dupes. The strap is also detachable. I just can’t believe what a great product for such a low price.
